Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: "Think of the cruelty Kamala Harris is inflicting on the people of Pennsylvania. You live in a small town your whole life, pay your taxes -- and suddenly, she flies in thousands and thousands of migrants from the most dangerous places on earth and they deposit them right smack in the middle of your community."
